  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Witnessed out-of-hospital cardiac arrest

          -  Non shockable cardiac rhythm

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Evidence of trauma

          -  Evidence of pregnancy

          -  Duration of no flow more than 30 minutes

          -  Rapidly fatal underlying disease

          -  Allergy to cyclosporin A
      </textblock>
